<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Option 3: Header + Micro Sidebar (Minimalistic)</title>
  <style>
    /* Basic reset */
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: sans-serif;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 50px 1fr; /* Micro sidebar width */
      grid-template-rows: auto 1fr;
      grid-template-areas:
        "header header"
        "sidebar content";
    }

    .header {
      grid-area: header;
      /* Removed background and border */
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 10px;
    }

    .header .logo-container {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .header .logo {
      max-width: 40px; /* Small logo */
      height: auto;
      margin-right: 10px; /* Space between logo and text */
    }

    .header .tpa-link {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #333; /* Or inherit */
      font-size: 1em;
    }

    .sidebar {
      grid-area: sidebar;
      /* Removed background and border */
      padding-top: 20px;
    }

    .sidebar ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding-left: 0;
    }

    .sidebar ul li {
      margin: 10px 0;
      text-align: center; /* Center micro-sidebar links */
    }

    .sidebar ul li a {
      text-decoration: none;
      /* Removed color, inherit */
      display: block; /* Make the whole area clickable */
      padding: 5px;
    }

    .sidebar ul li a:hover {
        background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.05); /* Subtle hover */
    }

    .content {
      grid-area: content;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    /* Removed specific styles, inherit */

  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <div class="logo-container">
      <a href="https://thepocusatlas.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="../images/vexus-ai-logo.png" alt="Vexus-AI Logo" class="logo" />
      </a>
      <a href="https://thepocusatlas.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="tpa-link">TPA Home</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="sidebar">
    <ul>
      <li><a href="#">Link 1</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">Link 2</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">Link 3</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h1>Option 3: Header + Micro Sidebar (Minimalistic)</h1>
    <p>This is a refined version of Option 3, designed for minimal visual impact and easy integration.</p>
    <p>The Vexus-AI logo and "TPA Home" text are in the header. A very slim sidebar provides navigation.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
